{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you have to be very, sort of, matter of fact, a correct relationship, because that was necessary for-- for negotiating with them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't need to salute like with the Hitler, sort of-- the Hitler way and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't need to praise them, at all, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had a-- we had a correct trade relationship with them and political, also, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what was the daily life in Berlin during that time?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to start with, in 1940, it was-- the food was rationed, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And and there was this-- they were-- you would think, perhaps, that they had-- in the spring of '40, they have conquered all the whole of Europe and all that, that they could live there in peace.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were bombed by the-- the British, by the Allies, not heavily bombing but-- heavy bombing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But enough for forcing the population down into the shelters nearly every night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that got on the nerves of the-- the population in Berlin, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I ask your pardon?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, on my level, of course, I really didn't meet those.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the-- up to-- to my boss and-- and the-- the-- the-- the Swedish officers, Swedish delegations, who came now and then to negotiate with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I observed this from a rather grassroots level, so to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really, because the-- the-- the Jews had more or less been deported, then, at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were non-- not existing in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't see many of them, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to start with, of course, you-- you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't have any authentic information about what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You suspected, of course, that something terrible was-- was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
